metadata.name: A woman with a natural disposition
metadata.description:
「Nature welcomes her, she welcomes art.」

size : 1536×1536 px

Background of Creation : I created this art with AI.
It has been a very long road to this point.
It was not easy to create the art I wanted.

With her talent for art and her gift of beauty, she looked as if she was welcome in everything.
But that is because she loved art so much.

I focused on why she was welcome.
